{
  "stem": "4764.4",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, I'm sure all of us think that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But I-- I personally think that I could have done much, much better, if only I would have had the strength of my convictions and believed in myself, that I was confident enough and, and, and that I was able to do things, which I didn't.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Which, obviously, I was able to, but I didn't have the confidence to pursue it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I had to curtail a lot of my activities.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I came back earlier than I should have.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I should have had more experience overseas.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I should have perhaps gone into-- more into academia, more into hospital work.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were lots of things",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a surgeon, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I married late.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I married when I was 32.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The reason for that was because, although my friends were married-- in those days they married very early-- I was one of the last ones to get married of my peer group.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] My parents were not happily married, for various reasons.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I think I didn't want to make the same mistake.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Plus, I didn't have anyone to really talk over things with, you see.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My-- my mother, god bless her heart, was very set in her ways, and you can understand why.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was no one.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I missed the fact that I didn't have any grandparents, or any siblings, or any, any close family that I could actually come to, you know, when I had my problems, you see.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I first, first fell in love with the first woman I ever fell in love with, I wanted to marry.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, my parents said, you're too young, you can't do it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I wanted to talk over this with someone that I could, you see?",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
